WEBVTT

01:06.540 --> 01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.220 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 12]

01:16.720 --> 01:18.450
I hate privileged connections most.

01:19.110 --> 01:20.580
Wuyue Court won't take you.

01:20.580 --> 01:21.580
[Wuyue Court]

01:37.670 --> 01:39.290
Do you long for Wuyue Court that badly?

01:44.030 --> 01:45.060
I never said your senior brother

01:45.080 --> 01:46.250
is there.

01:47.830 --> 01:49.340
I just wish to join them.

01:50.800 --> 01:52.220
Please show me a way, Mr. Hu.

01:52.910 --> 01:53.780
Although

01:54.240 --> 01:56.010
Elder Guangwei is my master.

01:56.360 --> 01:57.450
[Chongyi, Wuyue Court]
he picks disciples

01:57.640 --> 01:59.290
with extreme rigor.

01:59.550 --> 02:00.860
If you fail to impress him,

02:01.110 --> 02:03.090
you simply have no outstanding talent.

02:03.470 --> 02:05.620
You can’t force things.

02:07.440 --> 02:08.780
But I have a suggestion.

02:09.080 --> 02:10.580
Stay and assist Xiangxiang.

02:10.800 --> 02:13.250
Your cooking skills will be wasted if you're not a kitchen maid.

02:13.670 --> 02:15.250
I'd have accepted my fate a long time ago if I wanted to.

02:15.960 --> 02:17.570
I've struggled all the way here,

02:17.590 --> 02:18.460
so I can't turn back now.

02:19.870 --> 02:22.090
Hey, you two.

02:22.110 --> 02:24.570
I've been sitting here this whole time,

02:24.590 --> 02:26.060
yet you wouldn't offer me a bite.

02:39.990 --> 02:40.690
Young lady,

02:43.670 --> 02:44.460
it smells amazing.

02:44.670 --> 02:46.020
Can I have one skewer?

02:48.390 --> 02:49.500
It's all yours.

02:50.760 --> 02:52.370
Better than someone who mooches off

02:52.390 --> 02:53.300
my food all year,

02:53.320 --> 02:54.500
like roast chicken, roast duck, and roasted bird eggs.

02:54.520 --> 02:55.340
All my treats have gone to waste.

02:57.760 --> 02:58.250
Thanks.

03:05.520 --> 03:06.180
Chongyi,

03:07.080 --> 03:08.650
how long has it been since you had meat?

03:08.960 --> 03:09.850
You even asked for meat.

03:09.990 --> 03:10.970
Absolutely, I would.

03:11.320 --> 03:13.410
Even the flies in Wuyue Court cultivate,

03:13.960 --> 03:15.180
so there's no meat at all.

03:21.800 --> 03:23.570
You're Mr. Hu's elder,

03:25.480 --> 03:27.530
so you must be an elder of Wuyue Court.

03:28.960 --> 03:29.740
Well.

03:31.150 --> 03:32.020
You could say that.

03:33.480 --> 03:35.020
Will you accept me as your disciple?

03:41.240 --> 03:42.570
If you accept me,

03:42.870 --> 03:44.850
I'll cook all kinds of delicacies for you every day.

03:54.960 --> 03:55.970
I cannot accept you,

03:56.430 --> 03:58.410
but I'd never take advantage of you, either.

04:01.520 --> 04:03.690
You wouldn't ask me to spit the food out

04:05.640 --> 04:06.650
and I have no money.

04:07.110 --> 04:09.570
Hit me if that makes you feel better.

04:40.910 --> 04:42.210
It's time for me to leave.

04:43.680 --> 04:46.770
Except for the Dizang Sect, where else can I go?

05:16.120 --> 05:17.940
As a disciple of the academy and a mountain sect,

05:18.440 --> 05:19.420
[Lu Li, Wanxian Sect]
why act so cowardly?

05:26.470 --> 05:27.300
I, I just…

05:27.320 --> 05:28.250
You are bright,

05:28.520 --> 05:29.420
robust,

05:29.960 --> 05:31.010
and free of grave illness.

05:31.470 --> 05:33.130
If you belittle yourself merely over heartbreak

05:33.680 --> 05:34.890
and tangled love,

05:35.390 --> 05:36.500
that'll be sheer foolishness.

05:37.120 --> 05:38.210
You misunderstand. I only…

05:41.000 --> 05:43.770
Our life is to seek freedom above all.

05:44.640 --> 05:46.860
Free heart, unbound steps.

05:49.150 --> 05:50.450
Do not trap yourself in obsession.

05:52.790 --> 05:53.660
Who are you?

05:56.030 --> 05:56.980
A disciple of a sea sect?

05:59.150 --> 06:01.010
I'm Lu Li, disciple of Mr. Shen

06:01.470 --> 06:02.180
of Wanxian Sect.

06:14.960 --> 06:16.330
A heart broad as the earth sees clear truth.

06:17.000 --> 06:18.940
Step back, and boundless skies await you.

06:20.270 --> 06:21.130
I've said my piece.

06:21.710 --> 06:23.540
Take good care of yourself.

06:34.640 --> 06:37.660
Free heart, unbound steps.

06:41.200 --> 06:42.690
Wanxian Sect?

06:54.760 --> 06:57.100
Ji Tongzhou, Xingzheng Hall.

06:57.710 --> 07:00.890
Ye Ye, Baili Changyue, Dizang Sect.

07:01.590 --> 07:04.130
Baili Gelin, Wanxian Sect.

07:07.560 --> 07:09.770
Gelin, why are you…

07:11.760 --> 07:13.660
Mr. Shen's tortoise looks fun.

07:14.000 --> 07:14.980
I want to ride it.

07:16.590 --> 07:17.300
Gelin,

07:17.680 --> 07:21.060
I indulge all your usual tantrums,

07:21.150 --> 07:21.980
but you cannot

07:22.080 --> 07:23.250
mess around this time.

07:23.790 --> 07:24.620
Changyue,

07:25.230 --> 07:26.330
I'm already grown up.

07:26.760 --> 07:28.210
Let me venture out on my own once.

07:29.230 --> 07:30.010
I said

07:30.520 --> 07:32.210
let me choose for myself this time.

07:33.000 --> 07:34.060
Ye Ye, you and I

07:34.470 --> 07:35.980
can't stay side by side forever.

07:42.520 --> 07:44.810
Ding Sinan, Lantian Sect.

07:45.590 --> 07:47.940
Lei Xiuyuan, Wuyue Court.

07:51.080 --> 07:51.660
Okay.

07:52.030 --> 07:54.060
These are the immortal sects you will head to.

07:54.560 --> 07:57.660
The academy wishes all of you to attain the Great Dao soon.

08:01.390 --> 08:01.940
Madam,

08:03.880 --> 08:04.690
where is Lifei assigned?

08:05.470 --> 08:07.250
No immortal sect has taken her,

08:07.710 --> 08:08.570
so she skips this round.

08:16.790 --> 08:17.660
Skip it then.

08:18.120 --> 08:19.010
Straw sandals tread a thousand years;

08:19.200 --> 08:20.100
One dawn I roam the boundless sky.

08:20.350 --> 08:21.540
I refuse to believe there's no other way.

08:23.910 --> 08:24.770
Wait.

08:28.390 --> 08:29.130
Senior.

08:29.270 --> 08:31.570
You're weighed down by worldly desires,

08:31.590 --> 08:32.740
with no will to cultivate

08:36.350 --> 08:37.140
immortality.

08:37.560 --> 08:39.380
Why insist on joining Wuyue Court?

08:41.680 --> 08:43.780
Wuyue Court stands as the top cultivation sect.

08:44.200 --> 08:45.940
Admired by all, it slays demons and upholds justice;

08:46.830 --> 08:47.450
nothing compares.

08:47.710 --> 08:48.570
I must join it.

08:50.040 --> 08:52.300
As if Wuyue Court needs a bootlicker like you.

08:52.660 --> 08:54.450
How amusing, the things you say.

08:54.470 --> 08:55.180
Enough.

08:55.320 --> 08:56.850
If you won't tell me a single truth,

08:56.870 --> 08:58.660
this conversation ends right now.

08:58.920 --> 09:00.260
I won't waste words on you.

09:08.470 --> 09:10.210
What do you want this time?

09:11.960 --> 09:12.970
Join Wuyue Court

09:14.960 --> 09:16.180
to escape bullying

09:17.230 --> 09:17.940
and deception

09:18.990 --> 09:20.180
and to end wandering,

09:21.110 --> 09:22.060
cold nights, and rough meals.

09:22.960 --> 09:23.970
I long for full bellies,

09:24.630 --> 09:25.490
peaceful rest,

09:25.960 --> 09:26.780
and a free life.

09:28.590 --> 09:30.330
I wish to shield the ones I hold dear.

09:32.320 --> 09:33.330
If fate allows,

09:34.110 --> 09:35.570
I will follow our teachers' teachings

09:36.200 --> 09:38.090
to aid those lonelier and weaker than myself.

09:40.110 --> 09:41.690
These are my honest thoughts.

09:42.170 --> 09:46.480
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

09:47.400 --> 09:49.090
This sounds far more sincere now.

09:49.710 --> 09:52.300
Yet what you yearn for hardly differs

09:52.440 --> 09:53.690
from ordinary people's desires.

09:54.230 --> 09:56.300
What separates ordinary people from cultivators?

09:57.230 --> 09:59.450
All living beings hold the spirit of heaven and earth.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.570
Without an ordinary, calm heart,

10:01.920 --> 10:03.810
how can one cast off mortal ties and ascend to immortality?

10:03.810 --> 10:06.770
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

10:07.120 --> 10:11.680
♪Don't idle away time. We shall meet atop the peak♪

10:11.680 --> 10:13.300
You speak quite eloquently,

10:13.920 --> 10:16.090
yet we click well.

10:24.590 --> 10:26.850
Let go of your master's

10:31.320 --> 10:32.180
bamboo staff.

10:39.990 --> 10:41.850
I'm Jiang Lifei. Greetings, Master.

10:42.630 --> 10:43.730
I'll cultivate diligently

10:43.750 --> 10:44.810
and live up to your kindness in taking me in.

10:54.350 --> 10:55.380
Get real.

10:59.400 --> 11:01.540
I'll massage you every single day,

11:01.630 --> 11:02.690
and cook delicious meals for you too.

11:03.470 --> 11:04.490
Very well.

11:07.110 --> 11:07.610
She

11:08.510 --> 11:09.850
shall be admitted to Wuyue Court.

11:33.830 --> 11:34.900
Rest assured, Master.

11:35.440 --> 11:36.730
Once I arrive at Wuyue Court,

11:36.920 --> 11:38.330
I'll find Senior Brother

11:38.510 --> 11:40.330
and seek you with him.

11:56.990 --> 11:58.300
I'm admitted to Wuyue Court.

11:58.960 --> 11:59.970
Don't follow me anymore.

12:07.440 --> 12:08.780
I heard Wuyue Court has sixteen peaks

12:09.110 --> 12:09.940
with thousands of disciples.

12:10.590 --> 12:11.540
I can help you search for your senior brother.

12:13.470 --> 12:14.020
No need.

12:14.710 --> 12:16.140
You saved me during the graduation trial.

12:16.710 --> 12:18.020
Your debt to me is fully repaid.

12:18.870 --> 12:19.610
We are even now.

12:20.230 --> 12:21.300
No grace, no grudge.

12:24.680 --> 12:25.850
Just stay away from each other.

13:19.960 --> 13:20.610
Lifei?

13:21.280 --> 13:22.140
Why is she here?

14:21.280 --> 14:24.020
Kill her, and you may live.

15:15.470 --> 15:16.180
Lifei.

15:22.630 --> 15:23.330
Lifei.

15:51.320 --> 15:52.180
Lifei.

16:26.870 --> 16:27.690
Mr. Zuo.

16:40.280 --> 16:40.940
Lei Xiuyuan,

16:41.710 --> 16:42.940
your mind is ungrounded,

16:43.200 --> 16:44.090
and your fate is dim.

16:44.350 --> 16:45.380
You're prone to falling into the demonic path

16:45.920 --> 16:47.090
and being rejected by the world.

16:50.160 --> 16:51.090
To become immortal or a demon,

16:51.920 --> 16:52.850
neither betrays my true heart.

16:59.440 --> 17:00.940
The heart holds both yin and yang;

17:03.440 --> 17:04.780
good and evil hinge on a single thought.

17:08.990 --> 17:09.940
What my soul yearns for

17:10.680 --> 17:11.530
can never be darkness.

17:20.510 --> 17:23.580
To walk the world is to hold a torch through endless night.

17:24.360 --> 17:25.900
Your goodwill still lingers,

17:26.230 --> 17:27.340
and you are bold and resolute,

17:27.880 --> 17:29.100
so you may break free from this deadlock.

17:29.960 --> 17:32.770
Remember, what your soul yearns for

17:33.840 --> 17:35.730
is the right path for you.

18:15.680 --> 18:18.140
These slips are passes for all immortal sects.

18:18.680 --> 18:19.420
With these jade slips,

18:19.600 --> 18:22.340
you may report to your respective sects at the Mao hour.

18:29.840 --> 18:30.940
As we part ways,

18:31.160 --> 18:32.770
I shall leave you with a few words.

18:35.160 --> 18:36.660
Though you depart the academy,

18:36.920 --> 18:38.660
you'll always be its disciple.

18:39.200 --> 18:40.180
In all your future deeds,

18:40.360 --> 18:42.140
bear our academy's tenet close:

18:42.750 --> 18:44.900
Put yourself in others' shoes, and uphold justice and chivalry.

18:45.790 --> 18:48.420
Should any stray down the wrong path

18:48.550 --> 18:50.210
cheat, swindle,

18:50.230 --> 18:52.210
or spill innocent blood…

19:11.070 --> 19:11.690
Yet I trust

19:11.960 --> 19:14.140
all of you walk the righteous path.

19:14.750 --> 19:15.770
As long as you commit no evil,

19:16.200 --> 19:17.140
the academy

19:17.600 --> 19:19.380
will stand firmly behind you,

19:20.070 --> 19:21.250
supporting you all the time.

19:47.600 --> 19:49.010
How time flies.

19:54.120 --> 19:58.010
We'll all go our separate ways soon.

20:14.960 --> 20:16.250
We're leaving at the Mao hour,

20:16.710 --> 20:17.530
so we've got the whole night.

20:18.070 --> 20:20.860
Why not revisit Lugong Town together?

20:24.360 --> 20:25.140
Perfect idea.

20:25.510 --> 20:27.010
Before we enter the immortal sects,

20:27.510 --> 20:28.730
we may eat and drink

20:28.750 --> 20:30.010
to our hearts' content.

20:31.200 --> 20:32.970
Your Highness is the most thoughtful one.

20:34.030 --> 20:35.730
I know a few taverns in Lugong Town

20:35.750 --> 20:36.660
with amazing food.

20:36.920 --> 20:38.530
The only downside is the steep prices.

20:39.030 --> 20:39.660
Let's go.

20:40.550 --> 20:41.340
Go.

21:08.360 --> 21:09.010
Cheers!

21:13.880 --> 21:15.690
You can hold your liquor well, Your Highness.

21:16.200 --> 21:16.940
Enjoy yourself.

21:18.880 --> 21:20.140
Enjoy yourselves.

21:23.360 --> 21:24.290
Mr. Yan,

21:25.790 --> 21:27.380
what is the play putting on now?

21:36.790 --> 21:38.940
A tale of past lives, present days, and eternal love.

21:40.920 --> 21:44.420
Demon Lord and Flower Fairy are trapped in a fateful deadlock,

21:44.440 --> 21:45.940
doomed to fight till death.

21:53.680 --> 21:54.380
Look,

21:54.990 --> 21:57.450
the grand show is about to start.

22:36.090 --> 22:39.780
♪The warmth within my arms♪

22:40.160 --> 22:43.200
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

22:43.500 --> 22:46.900
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

22:47.260 --> 22:50.530
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

22:50.900 --> 22:54.100
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

22:54.420 --> 22:57.620
♪I can no longer tell you♪

22:58.020 --> 23:01.220
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

23:01.500 --> 23:04.540
♪Utter that line♪

23:04.900 --> 23:06.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

23:06.940 --> 23:10.860
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

23:12.220 --> 23:13.820
♪I still linger on♪

23:14.220 --> 23:18.420
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

23:18.820 --> 23:23.180
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

23:23.460 --> 23:26.420
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

23:27.750 --> 23:28.420
Hold me tight.

23:28.420 --> 23:30.180
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

23:30.540 --> 23:33.660
♪I wish you well♪

23:33.980 --> 23:35.660
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

23:36.020 --> 23:39.940
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

23:41.300 --> 23:42.940
♪You're still screaming♪

23:43.220 --> 23:47.540
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

23:47.980 --> 23:52.220
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

23:52.580 --> 23:55.420
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

23:55.740 --> 24:02.280
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

24:02.480 --> 24:06.640
♪Just to keep you safe♪

24:17.950 --> 24:21.640
♪My breath is about to stop♪

24:22.020 --> 24:24.790
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

24:24.790 --> 24:26.820
No one's here for this depressing play.

24:26.820 --> 24:28.760
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

24:30.070 --> 24:32.180
Born blessed by heaven, you know not mortal bitter love.

24:32.640 --> 24:34.140
Sorrow lends tales their allure.

24:35.510 --> 24:37.730
No beauty in unattainable love.

24:37.730 --> 24:39.480
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

24:39.880 --> 24:43.080
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

24:43.360 --> 24:46.400
♪To light your way through the night♪

24:46.760 --> 24:48.480
♪Knowing love and hate♪

24:48.800 --> 24:52.720
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

24:54.080 --> 24:55.680
♪I still linger on♪

24:56.080 --> 25:00.280
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

25:00.680 --> 25:05.040
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

25:05.320 --> 25:08.280
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

25:08.600 --> 25:12.040
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

25:12.400 --> 25:15.520
♪I wish you well♪

25:15.840 --> 25:17.520
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

25:17.880 --> 25:21.800
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

25:23.160 --> 25:24.800
♪You're still screaming♪

25:25.080 --> 25:29.400
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

25:29.840 --> 25:34.080
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

25:34.440 --> 25:37.280
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

25:37.600 --> 25:39.760
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

25:40.160 --> 25:44.680
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

25:44.680 --> 25:46.720
♪Who says love and hate♪

25:47.040 --> 25:51.840
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

25:52.080 --> 25:53.960
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

25:54.280 --> 25:58.560
♪Break the waves, no matter how mad it seems♪

25:58.880 --> 26:03.240
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

26:03.600 --> 26:06.480
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

26:06.800 --> 26:12.880
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

26:13.600 --> 26:17.160
♪To wander with you♪

26:54.920 --> 26:56.620
If you still forgive him,

26:56.750 --> 27:00.180
you'll meet a miserable death.

27:07.470 --> 27:08.940
All affection breeds torment.

27:09.710 --> 27:12.820
A wise person should cut all emotional ties without hesitation

27:13.750 --> 27:15.530
and never show mercy.

27:37.550 --> 27:38.140
Lifei,

27:41.200 --> 27:42.770
if life at Wuyue Court is unhappy,

27:43.120 --> 27:44.420
come to me at Xingzheng Hall.

27:45.160 --> 27:46.340
How could I ever be unhappy?

27:47.270 --> 27:47.970
Rather, you should

27:48.400 --> 27:49.940
stay vigilant in Xingzheng Hall

27:49.960 --> 27:51.690
and watch out for rivals plotting behind you.

27:53.070 --> 27:53.770
In three years at most,

27:54.310 --> 27:56.250
I'll become Xingzheng Hall's most powerful disciple.

27:56.640 --> 27:57.420
Of course.

27:57.990 --> 28:00.100
I shall rely on your guidance in days to come.

28:01.960 --> 28:02.770
If only you would ask.

28:08.120 --> 28:08.820
How about

28:08.840 --> 28:10.050
we reunite here three years later?

28:10.600 --> 28:11.420
Then we'll see who stands out

28:11.640 --> 28:12.820
as the sect's elite,

28:13.200 --> 28:15.180
and who slacks off with no progress.

28:17.990 --> 28:18.820
That sounds wonderful.

28:19.550 --> 28:20.290
In three years will come

28:20.600 --> 28:21.940
the once-in-five-centuries Sea Calamity.

28:22.470 --> 28:24.580
We'll gather again at Lugong Town

28:25.400 --> 28:26.250
to stand against it together,

28:26.920 --> 28:28.660
to live up to our teachers' hopes in us.

28:29.600 --> 28:30.140
Well spoken.

28:30.360 --> 28:31.210
Truly well said.

28:31.230 --> 28:32.340
- Regardless of all else,
- Let's share a few drinks.

28:32.680 --> 28:33.690
We'll meet again.

28:33.990 --> 28:36.180
We'll meet here three years later.

28:38.030 --> 28:39.100
Raise our cups!

28:40.600 --> 28:41.660
Wherever we may be,

28:41.750 --> 28:43.250
through perils great and small,

28:43.550 --> 28:44.490
we'll all come together.

28:44.960 --> 28:45.380
Deal.

28:45.990 --> 28:47.210
- Drink up! - Cheers!

28:51.470 --> 28:52.050
Xiuyuan.

29:02.230 --> 29:04.290
- Cheers! - Cheers!

29:30.440 --> 29:31.050
Who's there?

29:35.270 --> 29:36.010
Lifei.

29:37.550 --> 29:38.210
Lifei.

29:38.310 --> 29:38.860
Lifei.

29:39.360 --> 29:39.940
Lifei.

29:41.270 --> 29:41.860
Lifei.

29:42.440 --> 29:42.970
Lifei.

29:43.750 --> 29:45.100
Why won't you come with me?

29:45.880 --> 29:46.820
Name anything you desire,

29:47.360 --> 29:49.050
and I shall grant it all.

29:57.640 --> 29:58.210
It's so cold.

30:02.710 --> 30:03.970
Your hands were always warm.

30:04.920 --> 30:05.490
What's wrong?

30:09.990 --> 30:10.860
You're not Lifei.

30:14.470 --> 30:15.180
Who are you?

30:16.880 --> 30:17.690
My name is Miaoqing.

30:18.270 --> 30:19.620
When the Yange Hall was attacked,

30:20.030 --> 30:23.100
Your Highness saved my life.

30:25.200 --> 30:25.900
How dare you!

30:26.750 --> 30:29.290
You tricked me while I was drunk.

30:56.710 --> 30:57.180
Lifei.

30:57.920 --> 30:58.770
Have you spotted Gelin?

30:59.360 --> 31:00.210
She left before dawn broke.

31:00.230 --> 31:01.140
She left?

31:01.440 --> 31:02.690
Without leaving a single word to me.

31:09.550 --> 31:10.770
I packed pastries in this for you.

31:11.120 --> 31:12.100
Take them to Wuyue Court.

31:16.030 --> 31:17.580
What new storage treasure is this?

31:18.360 --> 31:19.770
It can hold all your belongings.

31:21.790 --> 31:23.690
I'll return to Duantu to see His Majesty.

31:24.840 --> 31:25.420
We will

31:26.510 --> 31:27.290
meet again three years later.

31:29.470 --> 31:30.180
By then,

31:31.030 --> 31:32.580
we'll grow immensely powerful.

31:39.230 --> 31:41.140
Back outside the Fragrance Chamber,

31:41.640 --> 31:42.420
you held back your blows.

31:43.120 --> 31:43.970
Let us make a pact

31:44.200 --> 31:45.340
to duel three years later,

31:45.510 --> 31:48.050
and settle once and for all who is stronger.

31:50.990 --> 31:51.490
Agreed.

31:56.160 --> 31:56.770
I'm off.

32:00.310 --> 32:02.010
Farewell, Lifei.

32:15.070 --> 32:15.690
Lifei,

32:16.600 --> 32:18.010
we're bound for Dizang Sect.

32:18.680 --> 32:19.580
Take good care of yourself.

32:21.400 --> 32:22.050
Take care.

32:24.070 --> 32:24.730
Farewell.

32:42.680 --> 32:44.210
Lifei, we…

33:00.000 --> 33:01.920
[Wuyue Court]

33:09.100 --> 33:10.640
[Zhaomin, Wuyue Court]

33:10.640 --> 33:11.450
Jiang Lifei?

33:14.920 --> 33:16.770
Drinking heavily, hungover.

33:17.030 --> 33:19.140
Peering about furtively, ignorant and unlearned.

33:21.360 --> 33:23.770
How can you tell that?

33:24.270 --> 33:26.450
Tidy up to meet our master with me.

33:27.310 --> 33:27.730
Alright.

33:30.480 --> 33:32.360
[Zhuiyu Peak]

33:36.920 --> 33:39.800
♪If legends tell of a perilous land♪

33:40.040 --> 33:42.640
♪Why not give it a shot and march with all my might?♪

33:42.750 --> 33:44.180
I'll beat you this round, hurry!

33:44.200 --> 33:45.010
Quick! Move!

33:45.440 --> 33:47.180
I'll place it right here.

33:47.200 --> 33:48.010
I'm winning against you today.

33:48.010 --> 33:50.200
♪Wearing a flowing green robe, like immortal feathers dancing♪

33:50.470 --> 33:53.040
♪The fierce gale is grasped tightly in my palm♪

33:53.120 --> 33:54.920
[Simo, Wuyue Court]

33:55.960 --> 33:57.920
♪Refusing to coast through life♪

33:57.920 --> 33:59.340
Zhaomin.

33:59.340 --> 34:00.310
♪Though a crisis is sealed before us, I will not give up♪

34:00.310 --> 34:01.420
Hurry up.

34:01.420 --> 34:03.600
♪Leaving my silhouette between heaven and earth♪

34:03.880 --> 34:04.750
♪Just as I hesitate and drift away♪

34:04.750 --> 34:05.770
Hurry up, let's go!

34:06.440 --> 34:07.100
Wait!

34:07.100 --> 34:08.480
♪A sudden awakening comes♪

34:08.520 --> 34:11.080
♪We will make all the world's pain kneel before us♪

34:11.600 --> 34:12.380
Zhaomin.

34:13.190 --> 34:13.900
Junior sister.

34:14.110 --> 34:14.820
Senior brother.

34:14.820 --> 34:16.400
♪The darkness all turns into illusions♪

34:16.400 --> 34:17.220
That was merely

34:17.400 --> 34:20.340
a short rest after a whole morning

34:20.880 --> 34:21.450
of rigorous practice.

34:21.920 --> 34:22.700
Now,

34:23.070 --> 34:25.170
rehearse the sword arts

34:25.990 --> 34:27.700
I taught you once more.

34:28.630 --> 34:29.700
Yes, Master.

34:29.700 --> 34:32.230
♪Guarding our ground, we rise to the peak♪

34:32.380 --> 34:33.960
♪No need to wait around for natural gifts♪

34:33.960 --> 34:34.490
Master,

34:35.070 --> 34:36.220
Lifei has arrived.

34:36.220 --> 34:37.700
♪Learning knows no end; we unite as one♪

34:37.760 --> 34:38.700
Zhaomin, you're back.

34:39.320 --> 34:40.380
They've practiced all morning.

34:41.880 --> 34:42.700
Take a break.

34:43.550 --> 34:44.610
Let me introduce someone,

34:44.990 --> 34:46.170
my new disciple,

34:46.670 --> 34:47.490
your junior sister.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.530
Greetings, senior brothers and sisters!

34:48.990 --> 34:50.570
Hello!

34:52.800 --> 34:53.700
Jiang Lifei,

34:53.800 --> 34:54.970
was your journey smooth?

34:55.470 --> 34:56.130
Yes.

34:57.840 --> 34:58.860
Came empty-handed?

34:59.400 --> 35:00.380
Of course not!

35:08.990 --> 35:10.820
This roasted chicken from Lugong Town

35:10.840 --> 35:11.700
smells amazing.

35:14.150 --> 35:16.340
Crab buns, preserved fruits, apricot cakes,

35:16.360 --> 35:17.740
and stir-fried nuts.

35:18.150 --> 35:20.130
I bought these to honor Master,

35:22.760 --> 35:24.780
and all of the seniors.

35:25.110 --> 35:26.050
Come on, take some!

35:26.400 --> 35:27.380
I get a share too!

35:28.670 --> 35:29.820
I want this one!

35:30.590 --> 35:31.650
- This. - I want this.

35:31.670 --> 35:32.260
Stop grabbing them.

35:33.320 --> 35:34.090
It's fine.

35:34.110 --> 35:35.260
Let them enjoy it.

35:35.510 --> 35:36.490
This tastes incredible.

35:37.880 --> 35:39.340
When I just passed the bamboo grove,

35:39.590 --> 35:40.170
I thought

35:40.190 --> 35:42.010
I could pick some wild mushrooms

35:42.030 --> 35:44.220
to make chicken stew with mushrooms.

35:44.510 --> 35:45.340
- Sounds great. - How's that plan?

35:45.360 --> 35:46.530
- Okay? - This dish is my favorite.

35:46.550 --> 35:46.940
Perfect.

35:59.100 --> 36:01.000
[Yaoguang Peak]

36:05.440 --> 36:06.220
Lei.

36:11.590 --> 36:12.300
Yue.

36:14.800 --> 36:15.610
Finally, you're here.

36:22.280 --> 36:23.490
You're new to the immortal sect

36:23.760 --> 36:24.700
with weak cultivation arts.

36:25.070 --> 36:26.570
Come to me anytime

36:26.590 --> 36:27.740
if you run into trouble.

36:48.510 --> 36:49.610
Are you looking for Zhuiyu Peak?

36:51.110 --> 36:51.860
May you introduce?

36:55.320 --> 36:56.450
Disciples of Zhuiyu Peak

36:56.800 --> 36:58.530
are known as the laziest lot

36:58.720 --> 36:59.570
among the sixteen peaks of Wuyue Court,

36:59.960 --> 37:01.090
idle and lacking ambition.

37:03.550 --> 37:06.220
Since Lifei has taken Elder Chongyi as her master,

37:06.470 --> 37:07.700
she shall hardly amount to greatness.

37:08.400 --> 37:09.900
You possess extraordinary talent

37:10.110 --> 37:11.010
with boundless prospects.

37:11.920 --> 37:13.780
Do not let personal affection

37:14.070 --> 37:14.900
hinder your cultivation.

37:18.400 --> 37:19.260
Merely a personal affection,

37:20.760 --> 37:21.820
do not trouble yourself over it.

37:25.440 --> 37:26.570
Since our first meeting at Chufeng Academy,

37:27.840 --> 37:29.090
you've helped time and again.

37:29.720 --> 37:30.780
I'm really grateful to you.

37:33.070 --> 37:34.170
Yet I cannot be certain

37:34.720 --> 37:36.050
if you really mean to help me.

37:37.510 --> 37:38.130
Of course.

37:39.920 --> 37:41.420
Our master personally chose you.

37:41.440 --> 37:42.340
It is only right

37:42.920 --> 37:44.010
that I look after you.

37:46.670 --> 37:47.530
Then may I ask

37:48.720 --> 37:49.610
where I can access disciples' files

37:50.360 --> 37:51.820
within Wuyue Court?

38:03.880 --> 38:04.970
Jiang Lifei,

38:05.190 --> 38:06.420
do you aim to starve

38:06.440 --> 38:09.570
everyone on Zhuiyu Peak?

38:10.070 --> 38:10.860
Hurry up!

38:11.400 --> 38:11.970
Coming.

38:14.030 --> 38:14.900
Quick!

38:25.760 --> 38:26.940
Master,

38:27.440 --> 38:28.700
Zhuiyu Peak hasn't had

38:28.720 --> 38:30.780
a proper meal in ages.

38:31.070 --> 38:32.260
Quit idle chatter.

38:35.760 --> 38:36.740
Let's dig in!

38:37.440 --> 38:38.860
- Pass some to me. - Eat more!

38:40.280 --> 38:41.090
Fill your bowls!

38:42.070 --> 38:44.220
Disciples from Cuihua Peak and Yaoguang Peak

38:44.360 --> 38:45.380
have all mastered grain fasting.

38:45.720 --> 38:47.570
Only you lot lack drive,

38:47.720 --> 38:49.380
thinking only of tasty food all day.

38:49.470 --> 38:51.610
No wonder Zhuiyu Peak declines year after year.

38:51.630 --> 38:52.260
Zhaomin.

38:52.840 --> 38:53.380
Thank you.

38:56.320 --> 38:56.970
This is delicious.

39:04.070 --> 39:05.260
Eat slowly.

39:14.800 --> 39:16.490
Are you full?

39:16.960 --> 39:18.450
I have something to ask you all.

39:19.360 --> 39:19.900
Go ahead.

39:27.670 --> 39:29.340
Have you seen this person around Wuyue Court?

39:30.630 --> 39:33.220
Is this really a person?

39:33.360 --> 39:34.050
Yes.

39:35.670 --> 39:38.090
He might look better in real life.

39:41.030 --> 39:41.900
Lifei,

39:42.190 --> 39:43.450
Zhuiyu Peak has the smallest crowd

39:43.880 --> 39:45.170
out of all sixteen peaks in Wuyue Court.

39:45.440 --> 39:47.700
Every other peak holds hundreds of disciples at least.

39:48.190 --> 39:50.300
Last year, Elder Guangwei counted,

39:50.470 --> 39:51.940
and there were thousands

39:51.960 --> 39:53.090
of elite disciples.

39:53.360 --> 39:55.050
We don't know every single one.

39:55.320 --> 39:56.380
- Yeah. - You don't?

39:57.360 --> 39:59.010
I'll check every peak one by one.

39:59.030 --> 39:59.820
Okay?

40:01.150 --> 40:01.860
No.

40:02.880 --> 40:04.650
Wuyue Court is a heaven-born secret land

40:05.150 --> 40:06.130
thick with spirit energy.

40:06.630 --> 40:09.010
Tempestuous winds swirl amid

40:09.510 --> 40:11.050
mist-shrouded peaks.

40:11.400 --> 40:12.490
Weak cultivators

40:12.630 --> 40:13.970
easily get lost,

40:14.630 --> 40:16.530
trapped for months or years.

40:17.320 --> 40:19.940
Just stay put on Zhuiyu Peak.

40:26.030 --> 40:26.860
Zhaomin,

40:27.110 --> 40:28.940
you'll send spirit jades to every peak.

40:29.150 --> 40:29.700
Then

40:29.720 --> 40:31.300
bring Lifei with you.

40:31.470 --> 40:32.940
She needs to greet

40:32.960 --> 40:34.530
all the peak elders formally.

40:35.070 --> 40:36.010
Master.

40:36.760 --> 40:37.900
As you take her

40:38.360 --> 40:39.130
with you,

40:39.550 --> 40:40.780
I'll have no worries.

40:42.070 --> 40:42.900
My tummy's rumbling…

40:44.400 --> 40:46.170
- Master. - Thanks, Master!

40:57.050 --> 40:59.640
[Ruzhi Peak]

41:01.670 --> 41:03.050
Hi, all seniors!

41:03.440 --> 41:04.220
These are

41:04.320 --> 41:07.420
Qingqiu Wugen cakes from Qingqiu.

41:07.440 --> 41:08.380
- Here you are. - Thanks.

41:08.720 --> 41:10.050
Delicious and great for sore throats.

41:10.440 --> 41:12.610
This peak's perfect, but so humid

41:12.630 --> 41:14.170
that it makes people inflamed easily.

41:14.510 --> 41:15.010
Here.

41:17.550 --> 41:18.090
Well.

41:19.110 --> 41:19.900
Senior.

41:21.320 --> 41:22.260
Try this Qingqiu Wugen cake.

41:22.760 --> 41:23.420
Wu Gen,

41:24.190 --> 41:24.820
Qingqiu.

41:26.990 --> 41:28.340
Ever heard of it?

41:28.960 --> 41:29.700
No.

41:30.550 --> 41:32.340
Is Wu Gen a place?

41:35.030 --> 41:36.570
Sort of.

41:37.760 --> 41:39.010
[Fuyun Peak]
Unlike our master,

41:39.030 --> 41:40.130
Elder Baifu of Fuyun Peak

41:40.470 --> 41:42.570
favors quiet cultivation and detests noise most of all.

41:43.150 --> 41:44.090
Wait here for me.

41:44.240 --> 41:45.420
Do not stir up trouble.

41:45.470 --> 41:46.740
No noises?

41:46.960 --> 41:48.450
Then I'll search quietly.

42:12.960 --> 42:14.530
[Deng Xiguang, Wuyue Court]
Unrecognizable across a thousand miles,

42:15.400 --> 42:16.970
yet follows close as the moon's shadow.

42:17.670 --> 42:18.340
Junior,

42:19.110 --> 42:20.380
the person you seek

42:21.360 --> 42:23.050
is related to the moon.

42:24.760 --> 42:26.260
How do you know this?

42:26.470 --> 42:28.260
Heaven's secrets must not be revealed.

42:42.200 --> 42:42.480
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.480 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:57.500 --> 43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

43:01.180 --> 43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

43:04.820 --> 43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

43:08.460 --> 43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

43:11.940 --> 43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

43:15.980 --> 43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

43:19.380 --> 43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

43:22.940 --> 43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

43:26.100 --> 43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

43:28.220 --> 43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

43:33.340 --> 43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

43:35.580 --> 43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

43:40.020 --> 43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

43:44.620 --> 43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

43:48.220 --> 43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

43:51.940 --> 43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

43:55.340 --> 43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

43:57.220 --> 44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

44:02.500 --> 44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

44:04.740 --> 44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

44:09.340 --> 44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

44:14.060 --> 44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

44:17.140 --> 44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

44:19.140 --> 44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

44:24.140 --> 44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

44:34.100 --> 44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

44:37.540 --> 44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

44:41.180 --> 44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

44:44.780 --> 44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

44:48.100 --> 44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

44:51.980 --> 44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

44:55.820 --> 44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

44:59.380 --> 45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

45:02.580 --> 45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

45:04.700 --> 45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

45:09.860 --> 45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

45:12.060 --> 45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

45:16.500 --> 45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

45:21.100 --> 45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

45:24.500 --> 45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

45:26.540 --> 45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

45:31.100 --> 45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪
